---
title: Cumin Quinoa Bowl with Black Beans, Bell Peppers, and Pepitas
description: Quinoa may be native to the area around Peru, but the versatile seed can be adapted to suit pretty much any cuisine. Here, we’re pairing it with a swirl of Southwestern flavors: black beans, corn, jalapeño, pepitas, and a dressing with cumin and lime. Flavor-wise, it’s zesty and citrusy with earthy undertones. But that’s just an added bonus in comparison to the protein and vitamin C that will help supercharge you through your day.
